OL,3,CFamily unable to grieve as online
OL,4,Cscammers target funeral
OL,6,FThe Long's are still coming to terms
OL,7,Fwith loss.
OL,9,FOn 29th May, their wife, mother and
OL,10,Fgrandmother - Rosilyn - died.
OL,12,FAs they struggle, like all families,
OL,13,Fwith the void left by a loved one's
OL,14,Fdeath, they've had to face another
OL,15,Fbattle - against online scammers.
OL,17,FOn the morning on Rosilyn's funeral in
OL,18,FGreyabbey, the family was targeted by
OL,19,Fsocial media swindlers, who attempted
OL,20,Fto get people to donate money in her
OL,21,Fmemory.
