OL,4,Cscammers target funeral
OL,6,FFake friend requests were also made.
OL,7,FIt has left the Long's angry.
OL,9,F"I couldn't believe it, it was the
OL,10,Fshock of it," said her son Stuart,
OL,11,F"that somebody could do it at that
OL,12,Fmoment in time when we were just
OL,13,Fthinking about mum, wanting to say our
OL,14,Fbye-byes and that was just taken away
OL,15,Ffrom us."
OL,17,FThe scammers used a post on Facebook.
OL,19,FNaming Rosilyn, advertising the time
OL,20,Fof the funeral, attempting to lure
OL,21,Fpeople in via a fake streaming link.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
