OL,6,F"I had received a friend request from
OL,7,Fthem while the funeral was going on,"
OL,8,FStuart added.
OL,10,F"So while we were sitting there
OL,11,Fgrieving as a family they were still
OL,12,Fsending people like me more messages
OL,13,Fto say here's a page, click on it,
OL,14,Fdonate on it."
OL,16,FThis sort of activity has come to the
OL,17,Fattention of some funeral directors.
