OL,6,FSome have even added a warning below
OL,7,Fdeath notices online warning people
OL,8,Fnot to follow links or to receive
OL,9,Ffriend requests from these pages.
OL,11,FThe National Association of Funeral
OL,12,FDirectors has advised mourners to
OL,13,Fcontact the family directly or funeral
OL,14,Fdirectors to confirm if posts are
OL,15,Flegitimate.
OL,17,FThe PSNI has also encouraged people to
OL,18,Freport any suspicious posts.
